{"id":618,"date":"2008-11-03T08:39:45","date_gmt":"2008-11-03T00:39:45","guid":{"rendered":"http://xbeta.info/?p=618"},"modified":"2008-11-03T08:39:45","modified_gmt":"2008-11-03T00:39:45","slug":"evernote-api-xml-script","status":"publish","link":"https://xbeta.info/evernote-api-xml-script.htm","title":{"rendered":"笔记软件EverNote更新: for win 3.0.0.899"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignright\" src=\"http://www.evernote.com/about/img/logo.gif\" alt=\"pic: EverNote freeware\" width=\"228\" height=\"60\" />EverNote｜<a href=\"http://www.evernote.com/\">官方主页</a>｜<a href=\"http://xbeta.info/tag/evernote\">介绍文章</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">注：EverNote v3 仍存在中文搜索问题，达不到 v2.2 中 *中文 “中文 任意匹配的程度，目前只能在搜索框输入中文字词，命中这些字词开头的内容。官方知道这些问题，但预计最早也要到2009年解决。</span></p>\n<h2>EverNote for win 3.0.0.899</h2>\n<p>★ 提升性能。不断提升性能，是EverNote每次升级的重要因素。这一版的EverNote windows客户端性能有了提升，响应速度更好，甚至启动速度也加快了。如果你符合下述条件，将可以明显感受到性能的提升：a）笔记数据库巨大；b）大量图片；c）大量标签（tag）。<br />\n★ 保存搜索。进行过搜索之后，可以在左侧面板右击该搜索，“保存搜索”，为它取一个名字即可。这一点不仅是你想象的那样方便。对于手持设备（比如手机、iPhone）用户，在桌面端创建一个搜索（更方便）就可以在手持设备上使用了。<br />\n<img decoding=\"async\" src=\"http://blog.evernote.com/wp-content/uploads/2008/11/win-savesearch3.gif\" alt=\"evernote\" /><br />\n★ 更好的pdf预览。笔记中含有pdf文件时，就算同时含有其他内容，如text、图像、声音，也可以正常预览pdf。一条笔记含有多个pdf也没问题。<br />\n<img decoding=\"async\" src=\"http://img411.imageshack.us/img411/9734/evernotepdfvf2.png\" alt=\"evernote-pdf\" /><br />\n★ 重新设计的图标。<br />\n<img decoding=\"async\" src=\"http://blog.evernote.com/wp-content/uploads/2008/11/icons.gif\" alt=\"图：EverNote\" /></p>\n<p>本文仅为rss输出提醒，阅读请至：<a href=\"http://xbeta.info/evernote-update.htm\">http://xbeta.info/evernote-update.htm</a></p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>EverNote｜官方主页｜介绍文章 注：EverNote v3 仍存在中文搜索问题，达不到 v2.2 中 * [&hellip;]</p>\n","protected":false},"author":2,"featured_media":0,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":["未分类"],"tags":["all"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https://xbeta.info/wp-json/wp/v2/posts/618"}],"collection":[{"href":"https://xbeta.info/wp-json/wp/v2/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https://xbeta.info/wp-json/wp/v2/types/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https://xbeta.info/wp-json/wp/v2/users/2"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https://xbeta.info/wp-json/wp/v2/comments?post=618"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https://xbeta.info/wp-json/wp/v2/posts/618/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https://xbeta.info/wp-json/wp/v2/media?parent=618"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https://xbeta.info/wp-json/wp/v2/categories?post=618"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https://xbeta.info/wp-json/wp/v2/tags?post=618"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https://api.w.org/{rel}","templated":true}]},"wp_type":"post"}